com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol.message.acknowledge

Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol.message.acknowledge.Record

  • public final class Record
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a packet record which is used in acknowledgement packets to indicate a packet was either acknowledged (received) or not acknowledged (lost in transmission).
    Since:
    JRakNet v1.0.0
    Author:
    Whirvis T. Wheatley
